snippet.title: Blow'em Out, Nintendo NES
snippet.description:
Blow'em Out for the Nintendo NES


Take on the challenge of blowing out the candles on your birthday cake. Watch out, though! The flames come to life!


For more information, visit www.second-dimension.com
